# Generated per-framework leaf output. codegen.mjs emits src/<Name>.<ext> +
# README/LICENSE into packages/<fw>/ as proof-of-emit, but the REAL leaf packages
# (package.json, build configs, dist) land in the distribution wave (a later plan).
# Until then this tree is pure regenerable build artifact — ignore it. The
# distribution wave will replace this ignore with tracked leaf packages on the
# @rozie-ui dist+source standard.
/packages/
